---
/** Proof of complex frontend work — trusted companies strip. */
---

<section id="proof" class="section-pad home-proof-strip" aria-labelledby="proof-heading">
  <h2 id="proof-heading" class="home-proof-strip__heading">
    Trusted with complex frontend work at
  </h2>
  <div class="home-proof-grid">
    <article class="home-proof-card">
      <div class="home-proof-card__logo">
        <img
          class="home-proof-card__logo-img home-proof-card__logo-img--invert-for-dark"
          src="/logos/autofleet.svg"
          alt=""
          width="160"
          height="32"
          decoding="async"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <h3 class="home-proof-card__title">Autofleet</h3>
      <p class="home-proof-card__text">
        React Native architecture and infrastructure work in a legacy production app.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="home-proof-card">
      <div class="home-proof-card__logo">
        <img
          class="home-proof-card__logo-img"
          src="/logos/monday-workdocs.png"
          alt=""
          width="200"
          height="43"
          decoding="async"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <h3 class="home-proof-card__title">monday.com Workdocs</h3>
      <p class="home-proof-card__text">
        Production-scale React editor work in a complex document system.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="home-proof-card">
      <div class="home-proof-card__logo">
        <img
          class="home-proof-card__logo-img home-proof-card__logo-img--invert-for-dark"
          src="/logos/healthy-io.svg"
          alt=""
          width="180"
          height="36"
          decoding="async"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <h3 class="home-proof-card__title">Healthy.io</h3>
      <p class="home-proof-card__text">
        Frontend work across regulated health-tech product and marketing surfaces.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
